      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FINE VIEW (6) is a promising dog in the frame at five of eight starts including two wins and was in the minors again latest (19.94) over 342m at this track. Has never missed the frame here from six starts. Looks the testing material here. LET'S ENJOY THIS (8) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Molley Macallan (20.13) in a TG1-4W. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Boxed out wide but fast beginner who can clear and cross early. Will give a great sight again. KILCOY LASS (1) led early but gathered in and found a bit of trouble before missing the frame with a 6 length fifth (23.70) in a TG1-4W at Gawler. Rates a leading chance. ADHANA LUKE (2) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
